<h2 id="alloying">Alloying System (Alloying Furnace)</h2>
<p>In MITE:BE, standard metal equipment can be <strong>upgraded through alloying</strong> in an Alloying Furnace. Alloying does NOT create alloys from raw materials — it transforms existing, <strong>fully-durable equipment</strong>.</p>
<div class="warning-box">⚠️ <strong>Critical rule:</strong> Only <strong>100% durability (intact)</strong> tools and armor can be alloyed! Damaged items cannot be smelted.</div>

