  <tr style="background:rgba(180,180,180,0.12)"><td><strong>High Carbon Steel</strong></td><td>Full-durability Iron tool/armor</td><td>Carbon Crystal Shards</td><td>High Carbon Steel tool/armor</td><td>Damage −5%/piece · Acid-resistant · Chain-Mining ability</td></tr>
